                                                                                              PE-03(03)       PHYSICAL ACCESS CONTROL | CONTINUOUS GUARDS
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              PE-03(03)_ODP         physical access points to the facility where the system resides are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              PE-03(03)             guards are employed to control <PE-03(03)_ODP physical access points> to the
                                                                                                                                    facility where the system resides 24 hours per day, 7 days per week.

