                                                                                              PE-03(04)       PHYSICAL ACCESS CONTROL | LOCKABLE CASINGS
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              PE-03(04)_ODP         system components to be protected from unauthorized physical access are
                                                                                                                                    deﬁned;

                                                                                                              PE-03(04)             lockable physical casings are used to protect <PE-03(04)_ODP system components>
                                                                                                                                    from unauthorized access.




